videos.description: Michigan State's Cody White makes a great catch for a 24-yard gain as he is pulled to the ground by a Maryland defender.
videos.headline: WR makes grab while being ripped to ground

videos.description: Connor Heyward gets a block and finds a hole for an 18-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Michigan State strikes first with 18-yard TD run

videos.description: Maryland QB Kasim Hill jumps on the errant snap, but Michigan defenders Kenny Willekes and Brandon Bouyer-Randle are there for the sack.
videos.headline: Michigan State's defense pounces on Hill for sack

videos.description: Brian Lewerke fakes the handoff and breaks off a big run, setting up a 33-yard Michigan State field goal.
videos.headline: Lewerke's 22-yard run sets up field goal

videos.description: The Maryland Terrapins take the field with a No. 79 flag and take a knee in memory of Jordan McNair before hosting Michigan State.
videos.headline: Maryland players honor McNair before game

videos.description: Connor Heyward bulldozes his way to the goal line before the ball slips free, but teammate Max Rosenthal is there to jump on it for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Michigan State jumps on loose ball in end zone for TD

videos.description: Maryland's Byron Cowart intercepts Rocky Lombardi's pass but fumbles just before crossing the goal line.
videos.headline: Maryland fumbles would-be pick-6 at goal line
